43:50.729 --> 43:52.929
All right.

43:52.931 --> 43:56.332
Farley: Come on.
Yep. There we go.

44:32.170 --> 44:34.904
Bo-tat understand American.

44:34.906 --> 44:36.339
Bo-tat,

44:36.341 --> 44:37.874
we're going to take you
to a beautiful land

44:37.876 --> 44:39.342
high in the mountains

44:39.344 --> 44:40.943
where you'll be
loved and respected.

44:40.945 --> 44:44.280
Where the air is cold and fresh

44:44.282 --> 44:46.716
and the water
is cool and sweet.

44:46.718 --> 44:48.918
It's the land where
you came from, Bo-tat.

44:48.920 --> 44:50.420
It's where you belong.

44:51.823 --> 44:53.990
Come with me.

45:57.989 --> 46:00.423
