46:00.425 --> 46:02.825
which means we're not
that far from tuy hoa,

46:02.827 --> 46:05.228
maybe about 10 Miles.

46:05.230 --> 46:09.232
We can get there tomorrow
and get ourselves a truck.

46:09.234 --> 46:13.770
An elephant on a truck for 150
Miles in the middle of a war.

46:13.772 --> 46:15.071
Piece of cake.

46:15.072 --> 46:16.371
Poole: Gilman, you know
those solid gold dog tags?

46:16.374 --> 46:18.074
They're yours.

46:18.075 --> 46:19.775
All you got to do
is get me out of here.

46:19.776 --> 46:21.476
Ah! Man, I just can't
spend the night in here.

46:21.479 --> 46:23.179
Just send... poole!

46:23.181 --> 46:24.447
Poole! Hang on a second...

46:24.449 --> 46:26.349
poole! Give me that!
What are you doing?

46:26.351 --> 46:27.550
Rustling up some
accommodations, captain.

46:27.552 --> 46:29.252
I can have beer and steak

46:29.253 --> 46:30.953
and... and padded cots here
in, like, half an hour.

46:30.955 --> 46:31.988
Maybe even some ice cream.

46:31.990 --> 46:33.356
And then, I figured,

46:33.358 --> 46:34.891
since you guys don't
really need me anymore,

46:34.893 --> 46:36.726
I could sort of head
back with the pilot.

46:36.727 --> 46:38.560
If all the enemy within 5 Miles
doesn't already know we're here,

46:38.563 --> 46:40.530
they sure as hell will
when a huey lands.

46:40.532 --> 46:42.865
Come on, give me a break, will you?
I got you the elephant.

46:42.867 --> 46:44.267
I'm supposed to be sitting in
the middle of a beach right now

46:44.269 --> 46:45.568
worried about my tan line,

46:45.570 --> 46:47.370
not out here in booneyville
worrying about snakes.

46:47.372 --> 46:48.938
Snakes? Snakes?

46:48.940 --> 46:50.907
You're right, poole.
You shouldn't be here.

46:50.909 --> 46:52.275
Give me the radio.

46:52.277 --> 46:53.876
I'll call general Richardson.

46:53.878 --> 46:56.445
I'm sure he can
get you reassigned.

46:58.383 --> 47:02.318
Break out rations, gentlemen.
This is home tonight.

47:04.556 --> 47:08.558
I'll bet you wish you had your lucky
bottle cap now, don't you, you smart ass?

47:24.475 --> 47:26.375
